# 🐾 Signature Game

# Animal Arena

## Overview

Animal Arena is a Summer Exclusive Open World Adventure.

The game only appears during the Summer Event.

---

# Open World

Approximately 15 different regions.

Examples:

- Beach
- Jungle
- Volcano
- Forest
- River
- Swamp
- Desert
- Snow Mountain
- Island
- Hidden Cave
- Ancient Ruins
- Bamboo Forest
- Flower Valley
- Savannah
- Crystal Lake

---

# Animal AI

Every animal has real AI.

Animals remember player behaviour.

Good behaviour:

- Feed
- Heal
- Protect
- Spend time together

Result:

Trust increases.

Bad behaviour:

- Attack
- Starve
- Hurt

Result:

Animal becomes angry.

---

# Trust System

Enemy

↓

Neutral

↓

Friendly

↓

Best Friend

Only Best Friends can:

- Ride
- Use Powers
- Receive Commands

---

# Commands

Players can command animals.

Examples:

- Follow
- Stay
- Attack
- Defend
- Sit
- Sleep
- Eat
- Drink
- Come

---

# Riding

When Trust becomes high,

Players can ride animals.

While riding they can:

- Explore
- Battle
- Use Animal Skills

---

# Evolution

Animals naturally grow stronger.

Players can speed up evolution using:

- Growth Potion
- Instant Growth Crystal

---

# Weapons

Players may equip animals.

Examples:

- Armor
- Machine Gun
- Rocket Launcher
- Laser Cannon
- Backpack
- Helmet

Weapons are expensive.

Ammo must be purchased separately.

